# <%= data.site.title %>

> <%= data.site.meta_description %>

This is the personal blog of <%= data.site.author.name %>. Articles are published at
permalinks of the form `/YYYY/MM/DD/{slug}/` and listed newest first below. The full,
paginated archive lives at <%= full_url('/blog') %>.

## Key pages

- [About](<%= full_url('/about') %>): About <%= data.site.author.name %> and this site.
- [Blog](<%= full_url('/blog') %>): The complete archive of articles, newest first.
- [Atom feed](<%= full_url('/feed.xml') %>): Machine-readable feed of recent articles.

## Articles
<% llms_articles.each do |article| %>
- [<%= article.title %>](<%= full_url(article.path) %>)<%= ": #{article.summary}" if article.summary.present? %>
<% end %>
- [Browse the full archive](<%= full_url('/blog') %>) for older articles not listed here.
